            <option letter="b">Theodore Roosevelt's volunteer cavalry</option>
            <option letter="c">Cuban rebels</option>
            <option letter="d">Filipino insurgents</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>The Rough Riders were a volunteer cavalry unit led by Theodore Roosevelt that fought in Cuba during the Spanish-American War.</explanation>
